    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321100/extras/fc407e29bbf3b42649b9cacc023c0515.poster.avif?t=1772025462\" width=780 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321100/extras/fc407e29bbf3b42649b9cacc023c0515.webm?t=1772025462\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321100/extras/fc407e29bbf3b42649b9cacc023c0515.mp4?t=1772025462\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CHAOSFALL – COLLAPSE IS INEVITABLE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spin. Score. Push your luck until the machine turns against you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every win feeds Chaos.<br>Every combo makes the system unstable.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play too well… and the game fights back.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chaosfall is a dark poker roguelite where massive scores awaken a reactive Chaos system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The stronger your run becomes, the closer everything moves toward collapse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build powerful hands. Stack multipliers. Lock key cards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chase impossible numbers before the pressure consumes the run.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321100/extras/56be4c4be1a5716f7b94ab96b2799054.avif?t=1772025462\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321100/extras_big/56be4c4be1a5716f7b94ab96b2799054.avif?t=1772025462 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What Makes It Different</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>🔥 </strong>Success makes the game more dangerous</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >♠️ Multi-row poker hands collide into escalating combo chains</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🃏  Jokers twist and corrupt the rules every run</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔒 Locks create powerful but unstable strategies</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚡Scores explode as systems stack beyond control</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💀Short, high-intensity runs built around risk and escalation</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321100/extras/aa29248d715769f8c844e4692b3653d0.avif?t=1772025462\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Chaos Is Not a Timer</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chaos reacts to <strong>how you play.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Repeat strategies → Chaos accelerates.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Optimize too hard → the system destabilizes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Push for one more combo → everything can collapse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is no safe strategy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No endless loop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Only escalation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321100/extras/ed5cdc5f052032ca968addb36eb3b4e5.poster.avif?t=1772025462\" width=800 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321100/extras/ed5cdc5f052032ca968addb36eb3b4e5.webm?t=1772025462\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321100/extras/ed5cdc5f052032ca968addb36eb3b4e5.mp4?t=1772025462\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Chaosfall isn’t about survival.  <br>It’s about how spectacularly your run ends.</h2>",
